All Implemented Interfaces:
Test
public final class RatNumSmallTest
extends TestCase

This class contains a small set of test cases that can be used to test the implementation of the RatNum class. For a more complete test, see RatNumTest. This class, RatNumSmallTest, deliberately omits some of the tests from RatNumTest, to permit comparing the effects of the two test suites.
